pullrequest.title: Move artifact origin to center of tunnel entrance

content.raw:
I see this:

```
[Err] [GameLogicPlugin.cc:711] [GameLogicPlugin]: Robot [X1] is too far from the staging area. Ignoring PoseFromArtifact request
[libprotobuf FATAL /usr/include/google/protobuf/repeated_field.h:1408] CHECK failed: (index) < (current_size_): 
[ERROR] [1564004616.663383691, 9.050000000]: Exception thrown while processing service call: CHECK failed: (index) < (current_size_)
```

‌

I’m still able to call the service after moving the robot back to the staging area though
